name: Jet de GO!
description: Jet de Go! Let's Go By Airliner is a Strategy game, developed and published by Taito Corporation, which was released in Japan in 1999/2000. As you play the game, raising your rank and gaining "miles" (the point system in the game), you can unlock several different aircraft to aid you in your travels. This game was also released on the Gameboy, and also ported to Windows by the Japanese video game publisher, UNBALANCE.
